snippet: A lead FBI agent in a sting that produced criminal charges against a state senator and 19 other people was removed from the case over unspecified financial improprieties, lawyers for one defendant said....

headline.print_headline: Lawyers: FBI Removed Lead Agent in Corruption Case
headline.main: Lawyers: FBI Removed Lead Agent in Corruption Case

lead_paragraph: A lead FBI agent in a sting that produced criminal charges against a state senator and 19 other people was removed from the case over unspecified financial improprieties, lawyers for one defendant said.
